# Bluetooth Hardware Setup (HC-05 Example)

## Components
- HC-05 Bluetooth Module
- Arduino Uno / Mega
- Jumper Wires

## Pin Connections (HC-05 to Arduino UNO)
| HC-05 Pin | Arduino UNO Pin |
|-----------|-----------------|
| VCC       | 5V              |
| GND       | GND             |
| TXD       | D2 (RX via voltage divider) |
| RXD       | D3 (TX)         |
| EN        | Not Connected   |

## Notes
- HC-05 default baud rate: 9600
- Use AT commands to rename device & set PIN.
- Serial data can be used to send unlock commands from mobile app to C program.
